    {
      "chinese": "傳說在洪水過後，族人下山時分成了三個支派：第一支沿著濁水溪而下的是鄒族；第二支沿著楠梓仙溪而下的是卡那卡那富族；第三支則是拉阿魯哇族。只有他往東方走，到一個叫「Hlasʉnga」的地方，遇到小矮人。",
      "ab": "amihla hlitimahla akuisa mataahla’ʉa tʉnʉmʉ rumahlaʉ, rumiacu a cucutahlana milalaucu caalʉ mutulu, cacihli ia muhluhlu sakʉrahlʉ sikunga milalaucu, ihlaisa Tapangʉna, siasasua ia muhluhlu sakʉrahlʉ hlamasia milalaucu, ihlaisa Kanakanavu, siatatulu ia ihlaisa tahlana Hla’aluana, tʉra a kana'ana musa mukakakua uruamitana miungu Hlasʉnga tarutʉahlʉ kavurua.",
      "order": "1",
